title: Luis wants Child Support from both birth parents as a tactic
description: I received a letter in the mail, after I posted my petition here, from the child support enforcement services stating Luis opened a case for us to pay him child support. He makes over 100k a year, I make 25k a year and child support should be court ordered not taken upon by the plaintiff's own discretion. He is using this a tactic to abuse, harass me, torture our family and to manipulate the courts to his favor.Â
